#

Herb-Crusted Pork Tenderloin with Creamy Polenta and Roasted Seasonal Vegetables

$25.5
650 kcal
Difficulty: 75%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

PorkComfort FoodGourmetSeasonal

Description

A perfectly herb-crusted pork tenderloin paired with creamy polenta and a medley of roasted vegetables for a comforting, elegant meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1.5 lb
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Chicken Broth: 4 cups
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan Cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Seasonal Vegetables (Carrots, Zucchini, Bell Peppers): 4 cups, chopped
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 1 tbsp
